    public abstract class AbsBoxingActivity
extends AppCompatActivity
implements Boxing.OnBoxingFinishListener
    A abstract class to connect PickerContract.View and PickerContract.Presenter. one job has to be done. override onCreateBoxingView(ArrayList) to create a subclass for AbsBoxingViewFragment.
